Package: cometh
Type: Package
Title: Analyse, manage and visualise co-methylation data
Version: 0.2
Date: 2014-02-05
Author: Peter Hickey <peter.hickey@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Peter Hickey <peter.hickey@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for analysing, managing and visualising co-methylation data.
    Loosely speaking, co-methylation is the correlation structure of DNA
    methylation.
URL: www.github.com/PeteHaitch/cometh
